{"an9.29:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 9.29 ","an9.29:0.2":"3. Sattavasavagga ","an9.29:0.3":"Aghatavatthusutta ","an9.29:1.1":"“Navayimani, bhikkhave, aghatavatthuni. ","an9.29:1.2":"Katamani nava? ","an9.29:1.3":"‘Anattham me acari’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an9.29:1.4":"‘anattham me carati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an9.29:1.5":"‘anattham me carissati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an9.29:1.6":"‘piyassa me manapassa anattham acari’ti …pe… ","an9.29:1.7":"‘anattham carati’ti …pe… ","an9.29:1.8":"‘anattham carissati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an9.29:1.9":"‘appiyassa me amanapassa attham acari’ti …pe… ","an9.29:1.10":"‘attham carati’ti …pe… ","an9.29:1.11":"‘attham carissati’ti aghatam bandhati. ","an9.29:1.12":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, nava aghatavatthuni”ti. ","an9.29:1.13":"Navamam. "}